text: Marko Jovanovski (born 24 July 1988) is a Macedonian professional footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Makedonija Gjorče Petrov. ==Club career== In his career Jovanovski also played for teams such as: Vardar, Teteks, Shkëndija, Pelister or Cypriot side Ethnikos Achna. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Skopje Category:Association football goalkeepers Category:Macedonian footballers Category:North Macedonia under-21 international footballers Category:FK Vardar players Category:FK Teteks players Category:KF Shkëndija players Category:Ethnikos Achna FC players Category:FK Pelister players Category:Sepsi OSK Sfântu Gheorghe players Category:FK Makedonija Gjorče Petrov players Category:Macedonian First Football League players Category:Cypriot First Division players Category:Liga II players Category:Macedonian expatriate footballers Category:Macedonian expatriate sportspeople in Cyprus Category:Expatriate footballers in Cyprus Category:Macedonian expatriate sportspeople in Romania Category:Expatriate footballers in Romania
